Summertime means festival time and peak season for EDM fans. With track by Hardwell, Martn Garrix & Jay Hardway, Lucky Date & R3hab, Dyro feat. Ryder, Justin Prime & Sidney Samson. On time by the summer comes here on Two CDs "Festival Anthems" with a total of 44 progressive festivals House to the boards which transform your sitting room into the next Tomorrowland! With high-carat and top-actual tracks of Hardwell, Martn Garrix & Jay Hardway, Lucky Date & R3hab, Dyro feat. Ryder, Justin Prime & Sidney Samson and to many many more!
